A full-stack web application built with HTML, CSS, JavaScript, PHP, and MySQL that facilitates home service requests. The system features three user roles: admin, client, and worker. Clients can request services by selecting the required category and a suitable worker, while the admin manages the platform and workers handle job assignments.
